<div class="bs-callout bs-callout-warning" id="callout-carousel-transitions">
  <h4>Transition animations not supported in Internet Explorer 8 &amp; 9</h4>
  <p>Bootstrap exclusively uses CSS3 for its animations, but Internet Explorer 8 &amp; 9 don't support the necessary CSS properties. Thus, there are no slide transition animations when using these browsers. We have intentionally decided not to include jQuery-based
    fallbacks for the transitions.</p>
</div>

